    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_111_1742-1830",
      "chapterUid": 111,
      "range": "1742-1830",
      "markText": "每当年岁凶歉的时候，人民没有本业可作，国家就应该进行宫室台榭的修建，以促进人民就业，尤其要雇用那些丧失了家产的赤贫者。这时候修筑宫室，不是为了享乐，而是为了促进就业，平衡经济。",
      "totalCount": 2214,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=111&rangeStart=1742&rangeEnd=1830",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=111&rangeStart=1742&rangeEnd=1830"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_192_2536-2633",
      "chapterUid": 192,
      "range": "2536-2633",
      "markText": "产权清晰化运动中的经营层暴富以及上千万产业工人的被抛弃，再次展现出中国经济变革的残酷一面：非均衡的发展造成非均衡的财富分配，在经济复苏和物质财富增长的过程中，基层农民及产业工人付出了最大的代价。",
      "totalCount": 2178,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=192&rangeStart=2536&rangeEnd=2633",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=192&rangeStart=2536&rangeEnd=2633"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_132_2151-2200",
      "chapterUid": 132,
      "range": "2151-2200",
      "markText": "一般而言，集权者用以鼓噪民心的理由大抵有四个：抵御外国侵略、防止地方割据、反贪反腐、反对贫富不均。",
      "totalCount": 1980,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=132&rangeStart=2151&rangeEnd=2200",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=132&rangeStart=2151&rangeEnd=2200"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_148_1412-1453",
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "range": "1412-1453",
      "markText": "这样一个道德高尚、百毒不侵的人，勤勤恳恳、日以继夜地把国家搞亡掉了，你怎么评价他？",
      "totalCount": 1910,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=1412&rangeEnd=1453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=1412&rangeEnd=1453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_160_1120-1174",
      "chapterUid": 160,
      "range": "1120-1174",
      "markText": "曾氏之虑是典型的儒家思维，经济发展的终极目的，不是繁荣商贸，而是维持均衡，稳定政权，稳定永远被置于发展之上。",
      "totalCount": 1404,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=160&rangeStart=1120&rangeEnd=1174",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=160&rangeStart=1120&rangeEnd=1174"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_179_2735-2823",
      "chapterUid": 179,
      "range": "2735-2823",
      "markText": "在整个计划经济时期，农民是一个被背叛和剥夺的阶层。他们失去了土地，被剥夺了进入城市的权利，他们创造的财富以“剪刀差”的方式转化为国家资产，而他们的生活质量却没有得到相应的改善。",
      "totalCount": 1392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=179&rangeStart=2735&rangeEnd=2823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=179&rangeStart=2735&rangeEnd=2823"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_105_1607-1619",
      "chapterUid": 105,
      "range": "1607-1619",
      "markText": "“统一是中国的一种文化”",
      "totalCount": 1260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=105&rangeStart=1607&rangeEnd=1619",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=105&rangeStart=1607&rangeEnd=1619"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_124_1545-1593",
      "chapterUid": 124,
      "range": "1545-1593",
      "markText": "极具讽刺意味的是，政府收入的增加并非因生产效率的提高，而是既有的社会财富在政府与民间的重新分配。",
      "totalCount": 1170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=124&rangeStart=1545&rangeEnd=1593",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=124&rangeStart=1545&rangeEnd=1593"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_112_1284-1300",
      "chapterUid": 112,
      "range": "1284-1300",
      "markText": "仓廪实则知礼节，衣食足则知荣辱。",
      "totalCount": 1164,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=112&rangeStart=1284&rangeEnd=1300",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=112&rangeStart=1284&rangeEnd=1300"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_110_2468-2528",
      "chapterUid": 110,
      "range": "2468-2528",
      "markText": "由政府控制资源所有权，然后把经营权下放给民间商人，以一定比例分配利润，这就是后世非常流行的“资产国有、承包经营”的雏形。",
      "totalCount": 1156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=110&rangeStart=2468&rangeEnd=2528",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=110&rangeStart=2468&rangeEnd=2528"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_110_3149-3197",
      "chapterUid": 110,
      "range": "3149-3197",
      "markText": "陈寅恪曾说中国的统治术中有“诈术”的成分在里面，管仲那句“取之于无形，使人不怒”便是最好的印证。",
      "totalCount": 1136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=110&rangeStart=3149&rangeEnd=3197",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=110&rangeStart=3149&rangeEnd=3197"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_131_1333-1383",
      "chapterUid": 131,
      "range": "1333-1383",
      "markText": "所有推行计划经济的人无不以“均贫富”和实现社会公正为口号，而实际上都是为了加强集权以及扩充财政收入。",
      "totalCount": 1050,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=131&rangeStart=1333&rangeEnd=1383",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=131&rangeStart=1333&rangeEnd=1383"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_110_907-977",
      "chapterUid": 110,
      "range": "907-977",
      "markText": "管仲提出了“寓税于价”的办法——把税收隐藏在商品里，实行间接征收，使纳税者看不见、摸不着，在不知不觉中就纳了税，而且不至于造成心理上的抵抗。",
      "totalCount": 1044,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=110&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=977",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=110&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=977"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_134_788-859",
      "chapterUid": 134,
      "range": "788-859",
      "markText": "中国历史上有过三次思想大解放时期，一是春秋战国，二是魏晋南北朝，三是20世纪初的民国初期，其共同的特征是，全数出现在中央集权瓦解或丧失的时期。",
      "totalCount": 1044,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=134&rangeStart=788&rangeEnd=859",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=134&rangeStart=788&rangeEnd=859"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_107_1375-1399",
      "chapterUid": 107,
      "range": "1375-1399",
      "markText": "所谓国家，从来是血腥竞争的产物，这是举世之公理。",
      "totalCount": 1026,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=107&rangeStart=1375&rangeEnd=1399",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=107&rangeStart=1375&rangeEnd=1399"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_132_2784-2847",
      "chapterUid": 132,
      "range": "2784-2847",
      "markText": "一场大的社会变革如同空间重构，疏处应可跑马，密处必不容针，王莽变法缺乏系统思考和风险预警，鲁莽激进，漏洞百出，失败乃题中之义。",
      "totalCount": 928,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=132&rangeStart=2784&rangeEnd=2847",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=132&rangeStart=2784&rangeEnd=2847"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_159_1251-1341",
      "chapterUid": 159,
      "range": "1251-1341",
      "markText": "通过比较便可以得出结论：中国的现代化并不是一场“迟到的运动”，迟到不是落后的理由。洋务运动之所以会功败垂成，甚至一直到今天，中国仍然没有成为一个完全的市场经济国家，则有另外的原因。",
      "totalCount": 923,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=235061&chapterUid=159&rangeStart=1251&rangeEnd=1341",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/37a329e053963537abbca8b?chapterUid=159&rangeStart=1251&rangeEnd=1341"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "235061_113_1818-1879",
      "chapterUid": 113,
      "range": "1818-1879",
      "markText": "儒家在经济治理上只有“三斧头”：一是“以农为本”，二是“轻徭薄赋”，三是“克己仁义”。遗憾的是，这三条在管仲那里都找不到。",
